Champion of Dark Powers		KEY:Drow ~ Champion of Dark Powers	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.DrowRacialTrait.DrowSpellResistance				PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Drow ~ Champion of Dark Powers],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.DrowSpellResistance]						SOURCEPAGE:p.24	DESC:Some drow offer themselves to dark patrons, particularly demon lords. Drow with this racial trait apply their spell resistance (SR %1) only against spells with the good or healing descriptor or against spells cast by a divine spellcaster who worships a good-aligned deity. Anytime a drow with this racial trait casts a spell with the evil descriptor, the DC to resist the spell’s effects increases by 2.|6+TL											BONUS:DC|DESCRIPTOR.Evil|2

